{"title_page": "Shorea pauciflora", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = EN\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = pauciflora\n|authority = [[George King (botanist)|King]]\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea pauciflora''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''dark red meranti''' or '''red lauan''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Singapore]]. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].\nThe [[Botanical name#Binary name|specific epithet]] ''pauciflora'' is [[Latin]] for 'few-flowered'.<ref>Allen J. Coombes {{google books|capqDQYT_VYC&|The A to Z of Plant Names: A Quick Reference Guide to 4000 Garden Plants|page=106}}</ref><ref>D. Gledhill {{Google books|NJ6PyhVuecwC|The Names of Plants|page=220}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite iucn | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea pauciflora'' | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33134A9761265 | date = 1998 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33134A9761265.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5479044}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|pauciflora]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Malaya]]\n[[Category:Endangered plants]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = EN\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = pauciflora\n|authority = [[George King (botanist)|King]]\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea pauciflora''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''dark red meranti''' or '''Red Lauan''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Singapore]]. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].\nThe [[Botanical name#Binary name|specific epithet]] ''pauciflora'' is [[Latin]] for 'few-flowered'.<ref>Allen J. Coombes {{google books|capqDQYT_VYC&|The A to Z of Plant Names: A Quick Reference Guide to 4000 Garden Plants|page=106}}</ref><ref>D. Gledhill {{Google books|NJ6PyhVuecwC|The Names of Plants|page=220}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite iucn | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea pauciflora'' | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33134A9761265 | date = 1998 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33134A9761265.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5479044}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|pauciflora]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Malaya]]\n[[Category:Endangered plants]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "-> lower case", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shorea_pauciflora"}
{"title_page": "Tamnagar", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the table at Infobox settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  -->\n|name                   = Tamnagar\n|other_name             =\n|native_name            = \u0924\u093e\u092e\u0928\u0917\u0930 \n|nickname               =\n|settlement_type        = subdivision of [[Butwal Municipality]]\n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  -->27\u00b041'04.7\"N 83\u00b023'49.9\"E\n|image_skyline          =\n|image_caption          =\n|image_flag             =\n|image_seal             =\n|image_map              = <!-- NepalRupandehiDistrictmap.png -->\n|mapsize                = 300px\n|map_caption            = Map of the village development committees in Rupandehi District\n|pushpin_map            = <!-- the name of a location map as per http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Location_map -->\n|pushpin_label_position = bottom\n|pushpin_mapsize        = 360\n|pushpin_map_caption    = Location in Nepal\n<!-- Location -->\n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Nepal}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces of Nepal|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Province No. 5]]\n|subdivision_type2      = [[Districts of Nepal|District]]\n|subdivision_name2      = [[Rupandehi District]]\n|<!-- Politics -->\n|government_footnotes   =\n|government_type        =\n|leader_title           =\n|leader_name            =\n|leader_title1          = <!-- for places with, say, both a mayor and a city manager -->\n|leader_name1           =\n|established_title      = <!-- Settled -->\n|established_date       =\n<!-- Area    -->\n|unit_pref                =  <!--Enter: Imperial, if Imperial (metric) is desired-->\n|area_footnotes           =\n|area_total_km2           = <!-- ALL fields dealing with a measurements are subject to automatic unit conversion-->\n<!-- Population   -->\n|population_as_of               = 1991\n|population_footnotes           =\n|population_note